---
title: Chinese-Style Chopped Chicken Salad with Dark Meat Chicken, Mandarin Oranges & Wonton Strips
description: This vibrant Chinese-style chopped salad combines tender dark meat chicken with a crisp mix of lettuce, cabbage, carrots, and radishes. It’s tossed in a zesty soy-ginger-orange dressing, then topped with juicy mandarin segments and crunchy wonton strips for a sweet, savory, and refreshing meal full of texture and flavor.
